{"tid":2442241,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人吹奏皇蘇嗰個亞歴山大PizzaHut (Isak)","createTime":"2021-03-11T08:47:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T12:14:51.000Z","uid":234509,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e2a2309109247a40bc16b03d4afd67adb2beda3e","tid":2442241,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T08:47:43.000Z","msg":"睇佢咁耐 呢條友根本冇缺點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明成米9高 但又步大力雄 又跑得好撚快<br />\n根本係白人版盧卡古 仲要靈活好多<br />\n而且唔係典型柱躉中鋒 佢走位都好聰明 又可以拉邊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5z7a9Ao.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5z7a9Ao.gif&h=369d9f39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋佢真係好撚大隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n盧卡古20歲嗰陣喺西布朗 我都有睇唔少<br />\n但都冇而家PizzaHut咁撼得<br />\n個黑人擺明存心衝埋去撞鳩佢 但反而係個黑人rip<br />\nPizzahut 仲要冇發過力咁滯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要射走個波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> cls<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0JQj2WK.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0JQj2WK.gif&h=0b0ffe77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n射術唔使講<br />\n18,19歲嗰陣隻左腳已經呯呯聲<br />\n當年法比加斯18歲 俾人屌射波好似交波俾個龍咁<br />\n點知去到23歲一發育完 即刻一季入19球<br />\n而pizzahut仲喺發育期&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cSaW5ax.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcSaW5ax.gif&h=20957aa3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住又粗中帶幼 啲小範圍技術好好<br />\n而家佢好多時都會俾幾個守衛圍住<br />\n但佢都有能力可以用小技術帶返個波出嚟<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VGuT7o6.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVGuT7o6.gif&h=1d82f7c4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J2qsspg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ2qsspg.gif&h=271bed1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲要有制空力<br />\n佢頭槌的確唔算太強 但啲力量都唔知喺邊度嚟<br />\n明明成200磅 一跳跳到九樓咁高<br />\n成個空中霸王咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CXbSDwq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCXbSDwq.jpg&h=7db35394&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後就係好重要好重要嘅球商<br />\n佢踢波好聰明<br />\n上面講咗走位聰明之外 佢轉數都好快<br />\n好多時面對後衛 都體現到呢啲急才<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MncObRy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMncObRy.gif&h=1eef0003&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d8GZ2Ye.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd8GZ2Ye.gif&h=0071dbc8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eC1fBif.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeC1fBif.gif&h=7fb346ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我覺得佢天份其實唔差過麥巴比<br />\n現階段都可能已經超越咗麥巴比<br />\n將來級數我覺得都會高過麥巴比<br />\n大吉利是講句 如果第時兩個都遇到大傷<br />\n我覺得麥巴比會廢咗幾成武功<br />\n但Pizzahut影響會細好多<br />\n<br />\n重點係佢而家得21歲&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n去到25歲 可能上面講嘅所有野都會level up咗<br />\n到時真係會怪物咁<br />\n<br />\n有身型 有速度 有力量 有技術 有射術 有地波 有制空 球商高 雙槍將 年輕 粗中帶幼 仲要靚仔<br />\n條友真係好撚痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n簡直完美男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7wTmwRU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7wTmwRU.jpg&h=ade8908f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3eOYy5f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3eOYy5f.png&h=d532fd37&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e3ccfe6e025f24cf5a2b9c3e329a458f74fa3d00","tid":2442241,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T08:54:42.000Z","msg":"樓主點睇莫哥哥(莫生)？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcSaW5ax.gif&amp;h=20957aa3&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcSaW5ax.gif&amp;h=20957aa3&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcSaW5ax.gif&amp;h=20957aa3&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcSaW5ax.gif&amp;h=20957aa3&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcSaW5ax.gif&amp;h=20957aa3&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcSaW5ax.gif&amp;h=20957aa3&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"afb6d3d079446fff3a17f60f1df6d5e75b3f2ee4","tid":2442241,"uid":79562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T08:56:32.000Z","msg":"樓主唔識波 負皮上一頁"},{"pid":"b6fe605d68c2757e99f5fb49007d6dde82439d70","tid":2442241,"uid":4895,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T08:57:29.000Z","msg":"睇GIF都覺得廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55ff974aac9a932149b1455068023a13ffe22f3e","tid":2442241,"uid":159653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6fe605d68c2757e99f5fb49007d6dde82439d70","tid":2442241,"uid":4895,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T08:57:29.000Z","msg":"睇GIF都覺得廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T08:58:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b68bfc0b989cfb42efa72bbba518b2a9e2eda41e","tid":2442241,"uid":1262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6